          "treatment": "HELPERR mnemonic: Help (call for assistance). Episiotomy (to provide space). Legs (McRoberts maneuver: hyperflexion of maternal thighs). Pressure (suprapubic pressure, NOT fundal). Enter (internal rotational maneuvers: Rubin II, Woods corkscrew, reverse Woods). Remove posterior arm (deliver posterior arm). Roll (Gaskin maneuver: all-fours position). If all fails: deliberate clavicle fracture, Zavanelli maneuver (cephalic replacement), symphysiotomy."
